narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Sick course. Take it if you can get in.
if you like the topic than yes. its a good class.

Many good readings in architectural history and the politics of planning. As is often the case in urban studies courses, student enthusiasm for particular projects makes for expansive and frequently rudderless discussion. You will be asked to write a few short papers and offer weekly reading responses.
